title: Levi's Men's 514 Straight Fit Cut Jeans (Also available in Big & Tall)
description: A straight up classic. Meet the Levi's bestseller that's not too loose and not too tight, it's just right. Levi's 514 Straight Fit Pants sit low on the waist with a regular fit through the thigh and a straight leg. Need an easy day-to-night outfit? Tuck in a button-down shirt and finish off the look with thick-soled boots.
